                        Lucie presented the Top 5 HR trends for 2024 that are currently shaping the labor market. She focused on the evolving role of HR, the
                        growing emphasis on people development, company culture, and the ability to respond to a rapidly changing work environment. The
                        discussion centered particularly on work force flexibility and, of course, the impact of AI on human resources.
                    </p>
